@node "Version history" "History"

                           @{b}@{u}Version history@{ub}@{uu}


   Stereo Crypter v1.0 (15-08-95):

     * Improvements:
       - Now,it's a real multitasking program    
       - Add the Quit option (no more Control-C check)
       - Add Quit crypting option
       - Add the AmigaGuide documentation

     * Bugs fixed:
       - Keyboard check was lame
       - No more Quit when you unselect the file selector
       - The crypter's engine worked only with four multiples' filesize


   Stereo Crypter BÍta version (??-02-95):

       - Pityful little buggy program
